      • canMoveToNextEditor

        boolean canMoveToNextEditor()
        Before open an editor this method is called to get the confirmation.

        Typically, the implementation would be like,
        • Check whether editor has any error or not.
        • If an editor has any error then get the confirmation message from the user. The return value whould be the end user decision.
        Returns:
        boolean
